# Dependency directories
# Nothing under vendor/ is tracked in git. Bazel fetches every module
# (public + private NVIDIA ones) through Gazelle's go_deps extension,
# which `go mod download`s them from GOPROXY at build time. The CI
# bazel job sets up a `git config url.insteadOf` rewrite using
# GITHUB_TOKEN so the private nvcf-go / image-credential-helper paths
# resolve. Local developers' own git credentials cover the same.
# Run `go mod vendor` locally if you want a complete vendor/ tree for
# plain `go build -mod=vendor` flows; it stays gitignored.
vendor/

# Editor / OS
.idea/
.vscode/
.worktrees/
*.swp
.DS_Store
